title: #139: The Octopus of Global Control with Charlie Robinson
description: Thank you so much for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli.  This episode we welcome author of the book "The Octopus Of Global Control,' Charlie Robinson, to discuss the tangle web that has become the internet.  Thank you so much for all your support!
